data.description: Must see this spacious and tastefully renovated home in person! All new exterior & interior paint. New flooring throughout. New toilets, sinks, hardware & fixtures. All kitchen appliances to convey. 3 full baths! Recently replaced roof. No front neighbors. Large Yard. Low tax rate! 5 mins to Tesla Giga factory. 15 mins to downtown Austin. Close access to toll road.
